WEBVTT

00:00.073 --> 00:01.615
<i>Previously on Mad Men...</i>

00:01.795 --> 00:05.229
This is over,
and not just this.

00:06.152 --> 00:07.557
You should get some sleep.

00:07.729 --> 00:10.145
How can I?
My wife's a big TV star.

00:10.798 --> 00:12.849
Why didn't you tell us
Frank Gleason was dying?

00:12.960 --> 00:14.634
Frank's going to be fine.

00:14.741 --> 00:15.971
I wanted to make it clear.

00:16.058 --> 00:18.533
Unless this works,
I'm against it.

00:18.640 --> 00:20.249
Just saying the same thing.

00:23.226 --> 00:24.833
So, how'd it go?

00:24.963 --> 00:26.292
We went in together.

00:26.418 --> 00:28.149
We won Chevy.

