35:47.139 --> 35:48.873
He has four watches.

35:48.907 --> 35:51.275
I'll know it when I see it.

35:51.309 --> 35:52.877
They're in the drawer
by his bed.

36:00.218 --> 36:01.818
Are we allowed to watch TV?

36:01.853 --> 36:03.487
I think she's lying.

36:03.521 --> 36:05.355
Are we Negroes?

36:05.389 --> 36:06.990
Will you put me through
to the police?

36:07.024 --> 36:08.892
It's an emergency.

36:08.926 --> 36:10.960
I'm at 783 Park Avenue

36:10.995 --> 36:13.496
and there's a stranger
in our apartment.

36:13.530 --> 36:14.998
What?

36:15.032 --> 36:16.966
No, I'm 14.

36:17.001 --> 36:19.035
My name is Sally Draper.

36:19.069 --> 36:20.469
Hello?

36:21.570 --> 36:23.338
Yes, sir.

36:23.373 --> 36:25.340
These children
ought to be in bed

36:25.375 --> 36:27.209
and they ain't
too well behaved.

36:29.678 --> 36:32.981
Yes, sir. They played
a joke on both of us.

36:34.050 --> 36:36.285
Uh-huh.

36:36.319 --> 36:38.252
Good night.

36:40.255 --> 36:43.090
Now why'd you do
something like that?

36:46.461 --> 36:49.297
You hurt my feelings.

36:49.331 --> 36:51.966
I'm gonna go out
and get some air.

36:52.000 --> 36:56.102
When I come back,
you best be sleeping.

37:33.105 --> 37:34.605
"This may be hard to believe,

37:34.639 --> 37:36.407
but the history
can't be ignored.

37:36.442 --> 37:39.310
The history should <i>not</i>
be ignored.

37:39.345 --> 37:41.979
Look, I don't want to waste
your time, with..."

37:43.647 --> 37:45.449
Peggy!

37:52.423 --> 37:54.591
"I don't want you
to shut this door.

37:55.926 --> 37:57.693
Just let me say a few things.

37:57.727 --> 37:59.061
You and I both know--"

37:59.096 --> 38:00.262
Did you want us?

38:00.297 --> 38:02.031
Yes.
Get everyone.

38:02.065 --> 38:03.899
No, wait.

38:03.933 --> 38:05.401
Just listen.
I've got it.

38:05.435 --> 38:07.503
Great.

38:12.842 --> 38:14.476
Remember this work?

38:14.510 --> 38:16.211
I've never seen it before.

38:16.245 --> 38:19.047
Well, it says it all.
It really does.

38:19.081 --> 38:23.317
Okay, I've got
this great message

38:23.351 --> 38:26.453
and it has to do with what
holds people together.

38:26.488 --> 38:28.522
What is that thing
that draws them?

38:28.556 --> 38:30.590
It's a history.

38:30.625 --> 38:33.527
And it may not even be
with that person, but it's...

38:34.729 --> 38:37.163
it's like a...

38:37.197 --> 38:38.698
well, it's bigger than that.

38:38.733 --> 38:40.767
And that makes them buy a car?

38:40.801 --> 38:44.604
If this strategy is successful,
it's way bigger than a car.

38:44.639 --> 38:47.507
It's everything.

38:47.542 --> 38:50.777
I keep thinking about the basic
principle of advertising.

38:50.811 --> 38:52.445
There's entertainment
and you stick the ad

38:52.479 --> 38:54.379
in the middle of the entertainment
like a little respite.

38:54.414 --> 38:55.848
It's a bargain.

38:55.882 --> 38:57.349
They're getting
the entertainment for free.

38:57.383 --> 38:58.851
All they have to do
is listen to the message.

38:58.885 --> 39:01.520
But what if they don't
take the bargain at all?

39:01.555 --> 39:03.388
What if they're suddenly
bored of the entertainment?

39:03.423 --> 39:05.457
What if they don't--
what if they turn off the TV?

39:05.491 --> 39:07.726
- You gotta get your foot in the door.
- Exactly!

39:07.761 --> 39:10.361
So, how do I do that?

39:10.395 --> 39:11.896
Let's say I get her
face to face.

39:11.931 --> 39:13.798
How do I capture
her imagination?

39:13.832 --> 39:15.800
I have a sentence, maybe two.

39:15.834 --> 39:17.735
Who's "her"?

39:17.770 --> 39:21.138
Promise them everything. You know,
you're gonna change their life.

39:21.173 --> 39:23.374
- <i>You're gonna take away their pain.</i>
- That's good.

39:23.408 --> 39:25.175
Then you hit 'em
with the one-two punch.

39:25.209 --> 39:27.010
What's the answer
to all of life's problems?

39:27.045 --> 39:28.078
A Chevy.

39:28.112 --> 39:29.980
No, it's not.

39:30.014 --> 39:31.481
Then it's oatmeal?

39:31.515 --> 39:33.483
No.

39:33.517 --> 39:36.653
What have you been doing
the last three days?

39:36.688 --> 39:39.122
Have you been working
on Chevy at all?

39:39.156 --> 39:40.991
I gotta go.

39:41.025 --> 39:43.493
You wanna get someone
in here who can draw?

39:43.527 --> 39:45.128
No, I don't have time for art.

39:51.368 --> 39:53.269
He's happy.
Now we can relax.

39:54.871 --> 39:57.039
You think he'll care
if I nap in here?

39:57.074 --> 39:59.141
Don? Wait.

40:24.899 --> 40:26.700
I'm going home!

40:32.713 --> 40:34.380
Okay, I'm gonna
change my shirt,

40:34.414 --> 40:36.515
tell Megan I'm going out
for cigarettes,

40:36.550 --> 40:39.351
then I'm gonna knock
on her door.

40:39.386 --> 40:41.854
Sylvia, don't close
the door on me.

40:44.224 --> 40:46.592
"When in the course
of human events--" no.

40:46.626 --> 40:49.628
"You haven't heard
everything I have to say."

40:49.662 --> 40:51.630
Don't shut the door on me.

40:53.933 --> 40:56.367
All right, all right,
he's home.

40:56.402 --> 40:58.436
Oh, thank God you're here.

40:59.739 --> 41:01.506
What's going on?

41:01.540 --> 41:03.273
I'll tell you what's going on.

41:03.308 --> 41:05.643
Some elderly Negro woman
held your children hostage

41:05.677 --> 41:06.877
and robbed you blind.

41:06.912 --> 41:09.379
- What?
- Betty.

41:09.414 --> 41:11.048
She robbed a bunch
of places in the building

41:11.083 --> 41:12.149
and she came in here.

41:12.183 --> 41:13.584
Our back door was open.

41:14.987 --> 41:16.954
She said she was your mother.

41:18.489 --> 41:20.323
We think we caught her
boarding the IRT.

41:20.357 --> 41:22.291
You'll need to come down
in the next 24 hours

41:22.326 --> 41:23.392
and ID your things.

41:23.427 --> 41:25.328
Because no one was here.

41:25.362 --> 41:27.831
Because she's off on the
casting couch and you're--

41:27.865 --> 41:29.766
what does he tell everybody,
that he's at work?

41:29.800 --> 41:32.568
This is not the time or the
place for this conversation.

41:32.603 --> 41:34.569
Ma'am, this could have
happened to anyone.

41:34.604 --> 41:36.639
Anyone who lives
in this disgusting city

41:36.673 --> 41:38.473
and leaves their
three children alone.

41:38.508 --> 41:40.709
Do you know Henry's
running for office?

41:42.211 --> 41:43.912
Sally, I'm really sorry.

41:43.947 --> 41:44.980
I should have been
home earlier.

41:45.015 --> 41:46.815
I want to go home.

41:50.786 --> 41:53.521
You get your hands off me!
I don't need to be manhandled!

41:53.555 --> 41:55.089
<i>I know you've
been holding out on me.</i>

41:55.124 --> 41:57.091
You don't know anything.
I defy your accusations.

41:57.126 --> 41:58.993
You peddle that ass
on the street.

41:59.028 --> 42:01.029
<i>You don't deserve a home.</i>
<i>You don't deserve me.</i>

42:01.063 --> 42:03.131
Yeah? I do fine
without you.

42:03.165 --> 42:04.866
- And you owe me money, not the
other way around. - Get out.

42:04.900 --> 42:06.166
'Cause I took
that boy's cherry.

42:06.200 --> 42:08.035
<i>$5, we'll call it even.</i>

42:10.304 --> 42:11.437
Is that true?

42:11.472 --> 42:13.473
No.

42:13.507 --> 42:15.308
You filthy, shameful,

42:15.342 --> 42:19.179
disgusting, shameful,
horrible...

42:19.213 --> 42:20.947
You're trash!

42:20.982 --> 42:22.614
You are filth!

42:22.649 --> 42:24.150
You know that you are!

42:24.184 --> 42:26.786
After I gave you a home,

42:26.820 --> 42:29.722
you go and do something
this disgraceful!

42:52.712 --> 42:56.246
I know you're exhausted, but I could
feel the floor swimming, too,

42:56.280 --> 42:57.981
when I came home to that.

42:58.016 --> 43:00.350
I'm surprised
we didn't all faint.

43:04.455 --> 43:07.257
I'm really sorry.

43:07.291 --> 43:11.094
Sally seems so grown up,
but she's really still a kid.

43:43.491 --> 43:45.860
- How are you?
- Busy.

44:25.630 --> 44:27.265
You should talk to him.

44:31.503 --> 44:33.171
Hello?

44:33.205 --> 44:35.439
I just wanted to call
and tell you I'm okay.

44:35.473 --> 44:37.407
I didn't have a heart attack.

44:37.441 --> 44:39.009
I've just been working
too much.

44:43.114 --> 44:44.647
I'm-- I'm so embarrassed.

44:44.682 --> 44:46.883
I acted like
a stupid little kid.

44:46.918 --> 44:48.919
No, you didn't.

44:48.953 --> 44:51.087
And I'm sure she's fooled
plenty of adults, too.

44:51.122 --> 44:53.023
She said she knew you.

44:53.057 --> 44:54.657
I asked her everything I know

44:54.692 --> 44:57.927
and she had an answer
for everything.

44:57.961 --> 45:00.830
Then I realized I don't know
anything about you.

45:03.300 --> 45:06.469
<i>Mr. Chaough wants to see you.</i>

45:08.905 --> 45:11.306
You did everything right.

45:11.341 --> 45:12.808
Try and forget about it.

45:12.842 --> 45:14.509
Okay.

45:14.544 --> 45:16.578
- <i>Bye.</i>
- Sally.

45:19.148 --> 45:21.350
I left the door open.

45:21.384 --> 45:23.284
It was my fault.

45:26.054 --> 45:28.656
Okay. Bye.

45:38.066 --> 45:40.167
I need to talk to you.

45:40.201 --> 45:42.168
Morning, fellas.

45:43.771 --> 45:45.972
I'm fine.
Thank you for asking.

45:46.006 --> 45:47.874
How could you bring
Frank's little girl here?

45:47.908 --> 45:49.709
I let her tag along.

45:49.744 --> 45:51.043
I kept an eye on her,
didn't I, Don?

45:51.078 --> 45:52.311
Who?

45:52.346 --> 45:54.213
Wendy.

45:54.248 --> 45:56.148
Believe me, it's a lot better
than what could have happened

45:56.183 --> 45:58.149
if I had let her loose in the
Village like she wanted.

45:58.184 --> 46:00.352
Well, that's not
what her mother thinks.

46:00.387 --> 46:02.053
What the hell went on
here this weekend?

46:02.088 --> 46:03.555
Half of this work is gibberish.

46:03.590 --> 46:05.190
"Chevy" is spelled wrong.

46:05.224 --> 46:07.259
Look, I am going
to continue on Chevy

46:07.293 --> 46:09.094
in my function
as creative director.

46:09.128 --> 46:11.263
That is, evaluating
other people's work.

46:11.297 --> 46:13.098
That's all I can do right now.

46:14.366 --> 46:15.867
Call me around 1970

46:15.901 --> 46:17.668
when they're ready
to make an ad.

46:17.703 --> 46:20.237
What are you talking about?
I can't do this by myself.

46:20.272 --> 46:21.539
I'm sorry, Ted.

46:21.573 --> 46:22.740
But every time we get a car,

46:22.775 --> 46:24.409
this place turns
into a whorehouse.

